# Personal Blog Content Exclusive License (Version 1.0)
**Copyright © 2025 一起游**

## 1. Scope of Authorization
1.1  Individuals are only permitted to view, browse and study all content of this blog for non-commercial purposes, including but not limited to articles, images, layout designs, copywriting materials, etc.
1.2  Any commercial use is prohibited, including but not limited to using the content for advertising, paid courses, commercial promotion, product packaging, paid reprints and other profit-oriented scenarios.

## 2. Prohibited Acts
2.1  Any form of modification, editing, tampering or adaptation (such as secondary creation, splicing, adaptation, etc.) of the blog content is prohibited.
2.2  Copying, distributing, forwarding, publishing or uploading the blog content to any public platform (including but not limited to social media, websites, forums, cloud storage, etc.) in any way is prohibited.
2.3  Applying for patents, trademarks, copyrights or any other intellectual property rights based on the blog content is prohibited, as well as claiming infringement by using relevant intellectual property rights.

## 3. Reprint Requirements
3.1  Sharing the original link of the blog content on personal non-commercial social accounts (such as personal Moments, private chats) is allowed; direct copying and dissemination of the content is prohibited.
3.2  If you need to reprint on non-commercial personal platforms (such as personal official accounts, personal blogs), you must obtain the author's written authorization in advance, and fully retain the following copyright notice in a prominent position of the reprinted content:
    > This article is reprinted from 一起游, Author: 一起游, Original link: [Article Link], Copyright © 2025 一起游. Commercial use and modification without authorization are prohibited.

## 4. Patent and Intellectual Property Protection
4.1  All intellectual property rights related to the content of this blog (including but not limited to copyright, patent rights, trademark rights) shall belong to 一起游.
4.2  Without written authorization, any entity shall not use the blog content for intellectual property application, rights protection or other acts; in case of violation, the right holder has the right to terminate the authorization and pursue legal liability.

## 5. Liability for Breach of Contract
In case of any breach of the terms of this license, the right holder has the right to demand immediate cessation of infringement, deletion of infringing content, and recovery of all economic losses caused thereby, including but not limited to attorney fees, litigation fees, compensation, etc.

## 6. Governing Law
This license shall be governed by the laws of the People's Republic of China, and relevant disputes shall be resolved through litigation in the people's court where the right holder is located.
